Package: memohelpR
Title: Helps you memoise R functions with the memoise package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Barnett", 
            email = "david.barnett@maastrichtuniversity.nl", 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1961-7206"))
Description: memohelpR is an experimental R package that provides an easy and efficient way to memoize functions. The main function, memoise_fun_in_proj, creates a memoized version of a specified function, writing the cache to disk in a folder in the project.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
